data.description: Boasting a generous 2300 square feet of living space, this home is designed to accommodate all your needs. The open floor plan creates a seamless flow throughout the house, ensuring versatility & an abundance of natural light. Custom upgrades include the 9' ceilings, double sided gas fireplace, sunroom & family room built in bookcase. Kitchen with a center island, new oven/range & dishwasher w/ tons of cabinet & counter space! 3 bedrooms + private office & 2 full baths. Primary suite offers a soaking tub, double sink vanity, separate shower, & walk-in closet.  Garage with 4' bump out, easy to maintain yard, & full brick front. NEW ROOF & AC! Close proximity to 465, downtown Indy within 15 minutes & Irvington within 10 minutes!
